name: Red Girl
description:
This artwork is part of the "Red" collection 
For a long time I have been trying to find colors that I like, a drawing style that has something to do with me, and today I can say that I have found it. 

The colors gray, red, white and black are part of the color palette of this collection. All composed of a red circle in the background, with details in red and white eyes, with beautiful hair in black and details in white and sometimes in red. 

I finally found myself, found my art style, adapted the grime art style to what I like to do and created a unique style that is only mine!
